snippet.title: There's NO WAY you WON'T LAUGH - The BEST ANIMAL videos!
snippet.description:
These funny animal videos are so hilarious that you won't be able to hold your laugh! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, horses, monkeys, pandas, goats,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things, feel guilty... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
